      • shouldInvokeAndWait

        public boolean shouldInvokeAndWait()
        Returns whether this command should wait for itself to finish running on the Swing GUI event thread. This is true only for graphical/GUI related commands that return important results that must be processed in an exact order.

      • shouldRunOnSwingEventThread

        public boolean shouldRunOnSwingEventThread()
        Returns whether this command should run on the Swing GUI event thread. This is typically true for graphical/GUI related commands.
